---
---
<section class="relative py-28 bg-[#0D0B08] overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Gold glow background effect -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[700px] h-[500px] rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/6 blur-[120px]"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#C9A84C]/20 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#C9A84C]/20 to-transparent"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16">

      <!-- Left: Text content -->
      <div class="flex-1 max-w-2xl">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#C9A84C]/10 border border-[#C9A84C]/20 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 mb-8">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C] animate-pulse"></span>
          <span class="text-[#C9A84C] text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">Voice Command</span>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] mb-8 leading-tight">
          Run Your Business<br />by Talking to It
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-[#9CA3AF] text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            You're driving to a job site and you get an idea that could save your company $50,000 this year. What happens to that idea right now? It goes on a note in your phone. Maybe a text to yourself. Then it sits there forever.
          </p>
          <p>
            What if instead, you pulled up your phone, said it out loud, and it actually got done?
          </p>
          <p>
            Your company's AI agent is always listening when you need it. Tell it what you want. It captures the idea, figures out where it belongs, and puts it into motion. If it's something your team should handle, the agent passes it down, assigns it, and follows up until it's complete. If it's something for later, it schedules a reminder. If it's something for the next leadership meeting, it adds it to the agenda.
          </p>
          <p>
            Owners and managers spend years building up a backlog of great ideas that never get executed. Not because the ideas are bad. Because there's no system to catch them and turn them into action.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold text-xl">
            This is that system.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[#C9A84C] font-semibold text-base border border-[#C9A84C]/40 rounded-full px-6 py-3 hover:bg-[#C9A84C]/10 hover:border-[#C9A84C]/70 transition-all duration-200"
          >
            See how it works
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Visual element -->
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-full lg:w-auto">
        <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-72 h-72">
          <!-- Outer ripple rings -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full border border-[#C9A84C]/8 animate-ping" style="animation-duration: 3s;"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-4 rounded-full border border-[#C9A84C]/12 animate-ping" style="animation-duration: 3s; animation-delay: 0.5s;"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-8 rounded-full border border-[#C9A84C]/18 animate-ping" style="animation-duration: 3s; animation-delay: 1s;"></div>

          <!-- Static rings -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full border border-[#C9A84C]/8"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-6 rounded-full border border-[#C9A84C]/12"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-12 rounded-full border border-[#C9A84C]/20"></div>

          <!-- Sound wave bars in background -->
          <div class="absolute inset-16 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/5 flex items-center justify-center gap-1">
            <div class="w-1 bg-[#C9A84C]/40 rounded-full" style="height: 20px; animation: soundwave 1.2s ease-in-out infinite; animation-delay: 0s;"></div>
            <div class="w-1 bg-[#C9A84C]/50 rounded-full" style="height: 32px; animation: soundwave 1.2s ease-in-out infinite; animation-delay: 0.15s;"></div>
            <div class="w-1 bg-[#C9A84C]/60 rounded-full" style="height: 48px; animation: soundwave 1.2s ease-in-out infinite; animation-delay: 0.3s;"></div>
            <div class="w-1 bg-[#C9A84C]/70 rounded-full" style="height: 32px; animation: soundwave 1.2s ease-in-out infinite; animation-delay: 0.45s;"></div>
            <div class="w-1 bg-[#C9A84C]/40 rounded-full" style="height: 20px; animation: soundwave 1.2s ease-in-out infinite; animation-delay: 0.6s;"></div>
          </div>

          <!-- Center microphone icon -->
          <div class="relative z-10 bg-[#1A1500] border border-[#C9A84C]/30 rounded-full p-7 shadow-[0_0_60px_rgba(201,168,76,0.2)]">
            <svg class="w-14 h-14 text-[#C9A84C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 18.75a6 6 0 006-6v-1.5m-6 7.5a6 6 0 01-6-6v-1.5m6 7.5v3.75m-3.75 0h7.5M12 15.75a3 3 0 01-3-3V4.5a3 3 0 116 0v8.25a3 3 0 01-3 3z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes soundwave {
    0%, 100% { transform: scaleY(1); opacity: 0.6; }
    50% { transform: scaleY(1.6); opacity: 1; }
  }
</style>
